{"word":"H3437 - יָשׁוּב - Yâshûwb - yaw-shoob' - Jashub","slug":"H3437","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָשׁוּב</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Yâshûwb"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yaw-shoob'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Jashub"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>ישׁיב ישׁוּב</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>yâshûb yâshı̂yb</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>yaw-shoob'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Jashub = \"he will return\" <ol><li>the 3rd son of Issachar and founder of the family of Jashubites</li><li>one of the sons of Bani who had to put away a foreign wife in the time of Ezra</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H7725\">H7725</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3142\">H3142</a>, <a href=\"#/H3432\">H3432</a>, <a href=\"#/H3433\">H3433</a>, <a href=\"#/H3434\">H3434</a>, <a href=\"#/H4877\">H4877</a>, <a href=\"#/H4878\">H4878</a>, <a href=\"#/H7725\">H7725</a>, <a href=\"#/H7726\">H7726</a>, <a href=\"#/H7727\">H7727</a>, <a href=\"#/H7728\">H7728</a>, <a href=\"#/H7729\">H7729</a>, <a href=\"#/H7731\">H7731</a>, <a href=\"#/H7780\">H7780</a>, <a href=\"#/H7870\">H7870</a>, <a href=\"#/H8666\">H8666</a>"}]}